<p>Scout, 28, paired her jean shorts with a white blouse that she wore with the sleeves rolled up.</p>

<p>She added two-tone beige and green shoes and had a white crochet headscarf over her long loose dark hair.</p>

<p>She completed her look by accessorizing with several necklaces. </p>

