<p>During her retail expedition, Scout dropped by a supermarket where she stocked up on some groceries.</p>

<p>She also picked up a large basil plant.</p>

<p>Scout is one of three daughters born to Hollywood stars Moore and Willis during their marriage which lasted from 1987 to 2007.</p>

<p>She has an older sister Rumer, 32, and a younger sister Tallulah, 26. </p>

