<p>Last week, Scout posted a sweet snap of her beloved pup Grandma to her Instagram and alongside it, she gushed about what the dog means to her. </p>

<p>'This dog...I cannot even begin to put words together to accurately describe my devotion to this magical, mystical creature that I have the sacred privilege of caring for,' she wrote.</p>

<p>'I consider Grandma one of my closest friends and despite the fact that I when I found her I wasn’t even interested in having a dog, she is the absolute dog love of my life! GRANDMAAAAAAAA I just love her so much.' </p>

